"1 1/2 cups (7 ounces) hazelnuts","6  large egg whites, at room temperature","  salt","1 1/2 cups granulated sugar","2 teaspoons pure vanilla extract","1/2 teaspoon pure almond extract","1 cup (6 ounces) mini chocolate chips","6 ounces bittersweet chocolate, melted and cooled","3 cups heavy cream","1/4 cup confectioners' sugar","  Chocolate shavings, for garnish"